  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1023">
<l>kuṭiceyva leṉṉu moruvaṟkut teyva</l>
<l>maṭitaṟṟut tāṉmun tuṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Deity will clothe itself and appear before him who resolves on raising his family.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
